title: Climate Prediction Center (CPC) Monitoring of Global Monsoons
name: climate-prediction-center-cpc-monitoring-of-global-monsoons
notes: Patterns of totals (or means) and their anomalies in the past week (or pentad for precipitation and outgoing longwave radiation - OLR), month, and season are shown for sea surface temperature (SST), 200-mb winds, 850-mb winds, 200-mb velocity potential, soil moisture, precipitation, OLR, and 2-meter air temperature.

Anomaly of 200-hPa velocity potential (shading) and divergent winds (vectors) for the 30-day period from 30 December 2011 to 28 January 2012. The reference climatological period is 1981-2010.
